column2: For more information on the fee description, please go to https://www.elavon.ca/coc
All transactions you submit, including credits/returns, require a valid
authorization from Elavon and the card issuing bank. To comply with card
brand rules, beginning in April, transactions you submit without a valid
authorization obtained through Elavon may be declined or voided.
*Fees Paid consist of Discount and Per Item Fees, Authorization Fees, and Card Association Assessment Fees
